Package org.jboss.windup.reporting.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationReportIndexService
    Service methods for finding and creating ApplicationReportIndexModel objects.
    ApplicationReportService
    This class provides helpful utility methods for creating and finding ApplicationReportModel vertices.
    ClassificationService
    Adds methods for loading and querying ClassificationModel related data.
    InlineHintService
    This provides helper functions for finding and creating BlackListModels within the graph.
    ReportService
    Convenient search and creation methods for ReportModel.
    SourceReportModelService
    This provides helper queries and functions for finding and creating SourceReportModel instances.
    TechnologyTagService
    Contains methods for finding, creating, and deleting TechnologyTagModel instances.
